                <div className="space-y-2 text-sm">
                  <p className="font-medium">To enable 3D features:</p>
                  <ul className="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-muted-foreground">
                    <li>Use a modern browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)</li>
